"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The BBC talked to people living in Havana after the US accused Ra\u00fal Castro, Cuba's former leader, of murder. Cuba's foreign minister said that Rubio was trying to start a military attack.\",            \"english_title\": \"US Accuses Ra\u00fal Castro\",            \"translated_version\": \"La BBC habl\u00f3 con personas que viven en La Habana despu\u00e9s de que EE.UU. acus\u00f3 a Ra\u00fal Castro, el exl\u00edder de Cuba, de asesinato. El ministro de relaciones exteriores de Cuba dijo que Rubio estaba tratando de comenzar un ataque militar.\",            \"translated_title\": \"EE.UU. acusa a Ra\u00fal Castro\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Voters in a western province will decide next October if they want to stay in Canada or start a process for an independence vote.\",            \"english_title\": \"Province Votes on Independence\",            \"translated_version\": \"Los votantes en una provincia del oeste decidir\u00e1n el pr\u00f3ximo octubre si quieren quedarse en Canad\u00e1 o comenzar un proceso para un voto de independencia.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Provincia vota sobre independencia\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Petrini's movement is against fast food and supports sustainable production and traditional cooking.\",            \"english_title\": \"Petrini's Movement Against Fast Food\",            \"translated_version\": \"El movimiento de Petrini est\u00e1 en contra de la comida r\u00e1pida y apoya la producci\u00f3n sostenible y la cocina tradicional.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Movimiento de Petrini contra comida r\u00e1pida\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Police are looking for a YouTuber who is accused of making up evidence to harm actor Kim Soo-hyun's reputation.\",            \"english_title\": \"Police Search for YouTuber\",            \"translated_version\": \"La polic\u00eda busca a un YouTuber acusado de inventar pruebas para da\u00f1ar la reputaci\u00f3n del actor Kim Soo-hyun.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Polic\u00eda busca a YouTuber\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The India-Africa summit is planned to happen next week in Delhi after more than ten years.\",            \"english_title\": \"India-Africa Summit in Delhi\",            \"translated_version\": \"La cumbre India-\u00c1frica est\u00e1 planeada para la pr\u00f3xima semana en Delhi despu\u00e9s de m\u00e1s de diez a\u00f1os.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Cumbre India-\u00c1frica en Delhi\"        }    ]}"